1.2.15 PEP 3129: Class Decorators
---------------------------------

Decorators have been extended from functions to classes.  It's now
legal to write:

    @foo
    @bar
    class A:
      pass

This is equivalent to:

    class A:
      pass

    A = foo(bar(A))


